{"tid":2321090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Fox ：白登弟弟詹姆士正在接受FBI調查","createTime":"2020-12-11T09:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T09:21:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c538e0ab69e638a1c46e5cc367eadbe6599a97b7","tid":2321090,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QFqGqJIQZzSFcN4W5F4VbA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTgxOC45OTA0NTAyMDQ2Mzg1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/SMLljj4jTE8DBQ8bJZQPlw--~B/aD05Mzg7dz03MzM7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/newtalk.tw/e093f575ff515a8fc3144d929f58bc95\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQFqGqJIQZzSFcN4W5F4VbA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTgxOC45OTA0NTAyMDQ2Mzg1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSMLljj4jTE8DBQ8bJZQPlw--~B%2FaD05Mzg7dz03MzM7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fe093f575ff515a8fc3144d929f58bc95&h=5a22c3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統當選人喬&middot;拜登（Joe Biden）其胞弟詹姆士&middot;拜登（James Biden）正在接受美國聯邦調查局（FBI）調查。 圖 : 翻攝自秦鵬B推特<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據福斯新聞《Fox News》當地時間10日報導，美國總統當選人喬&middot;拜登（Joe Biden）其胞弟詹姆士&middot;拜登（James Biden）正在接受美國聯邦調查局（FBI）調查。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報導，兩名知情調查人士透露，賓州西部地區相關部門正在調查一間已經破產的美國一健保公司，並且詢問詹姆士&middot;拜登於該公司的角色。<br />\n<br />\n當地時間9日報導，拜登次子杭特（Hunter Biden）選後因「稅務問題」，遭到德拉瓦州的聯邦檢察官調查。杭特於聲明表示 :「我非常認真看待這一問題，但我有信心，對這些問題進行專業而客觀的審查，將可證明我合法適當的處理我的稅務」，杭特並未透露調查其他細節。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RsWiX0MJLWYRZOIYSsvk2g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTU3MC40/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/25a_PAvGeLC330Vx3JRtPw--~B/aD03MTM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/newtalk.tw/530c761978478c9b665069593f07260e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRsWiX0MJLWYRZOIYSsvk2g--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTU3MC40%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F25a_PAvGeLC330Vx3JRtPw--~B%2FaD03MTM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewtalk.tw%2F530c761978478c9b665069593f07260e&h=35de2616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拜登兒子杭特發聲明表示，現在正接受稅務調查。 圖：翻攝自維基網站（資料照）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/福斯新聞-拜登弟弟詹姆士正在接受fbi調查-085146153.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E7%A6%8F%E6%96%AF%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E5%BC%9F%E5%BC%9F%E8%A9%B9%E5%A7%86%E5%A3%AB%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97fbi%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-085146153.html&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=51a3c198\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/福斯新聞-拜登弟弟詹姆士正在接受fbi調查-085146153.html</a>"},{"pid":"96c09655f594369ffb397165f5d150160867fe08","tid":2321090,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:21:09.000Z","msg":"借位求 pin 5毛好驚 Twitter 多人玩, 一有 Twitter post 就唔見5毛<br />\nTwitter 戰線需要大家!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2321042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2321042</a>"}]}